## Phase 3: Fix Lint Warnings

### 3.1 `list.ts` - O(n²) accumulating spread

**File**: `packages/tools/src/helpers/list.ts`

**Fix**: Use Object.assign with correct guard
```typescript
export function reduce<Result, const Item>(
  items: ReadonlyArray<Item>,
  reducer: (next: Item) => Partial<Result> | undefined,
): Result {
  const result = {} as Result;
  for (const item of items) {
    const next = reducer(item);
    if (next !== undefined) {
      Object.assign(result, next);
    }
  }
  return result;
}
```

